<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink312">
<l>aṟañcā liyarō vaṟañcā liyarō</l>
<l>vaṟaṉuṇ ṭāyiṉu maṟañcā liyarō</l>
<l>vāḷvaṉap puṟṟa varuvik</l>
<l>kōḷva leṉṉaiyai maṟaitta kuṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Let virtue abound, let virtue abound!</l>
<l>And even if drought happens, let virtue abound</l>
<l>in the hills with waterfalls of splendid beauty,</l>
<l>that concealed my man capable of killing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
